data.value:
Got your back up? was developed after the Information Services Branch (ISB aka the InSurmountable Barrier) refused to install a backup progam to allow us to make backups of work on our local drives.
To be fair, there was no refusal per se, just a process of attrition over six months that eventually ground us down.
Whence the name? Well, while ISB did not provide us with a backup solution, it certainly got my back up!
